## 5. Benefits for AGI Safety

Prevents catastrophic shortcuts, reveals adversarial exploit surfaces, neutralizes ego-driven reasoning, maps failure before failure, stabilizes narrative arcs, prevents escalation loops, reduces destructive impulses, and enforces ethical continuity.

**This is antifragile ethical design.**

